usage : tty-clock [-iuvSbahDxn] [-C [0-7]] [-f format]
    -x            Show box                                       
    -C [0-7]      Set the clock color                            
    -b            Use bold colors                                
    -f format     Set the date format                            
    -n            Don't quit on keypress                         
    -v            Show tty-clock version                         
    -i            Show some info about tty-clock                 
    -h            Show this page                                 
    -D            Hide date                                      
